name: Bitcat
description: BITCAT: The Prosperous Cat Blesses Bitcoin. Born alongside Bitcoin, BITCAT is the mystical feline guardian of the blockchain. With its 9 lives, it symbolizes Bitcoin's strength, precision, and infinite potential. BITCAT safeguards your wealth, ensuring luck and prosperity flow with every transaction. Legend says it watches over block number nine, blessing the network with abundance and security. Join the BITCAT community and let this charming cat guide your journey to financial freedom. Embrace BITCAT, the mascot of Bitcoin!
